  <brief_title>Cardiovascular Evaluation Before Renal Transplantation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Cardiovascular Diagnostic Before Renal Transplantation: a Prospective Study to Assess Cardiovascular Morbidity Before Renal Transplantation and to Improve Standard Diagnostic Procedures.</official_title>
